  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion:

          -  &gt;18 and legally fit for consent

          -  Symptomatic hallux valgus with HVA &gt;15 degrees

        Exclusion:

          -  Active physical or mental disorders that could affect rehabilitation including

               -  Other conditions affecting ambulation: lower limb injury, neuromuscular problems
                  etc.

               -  Mental incapacitation

